# Static Site Configuration for Render

## Build Settings
- Build Command: `npm run build`
- Publish Directory: `../dist`
- Environment: Static Site

## Environment Variables
- REACT_APP_API_URL: https://school-crm-backend.onrender.com/api
- REACT_APP_ENVIRONMENT: production

## Important Notes
- This build uses a custom build.js script to properly handle environment variables
- All API calls are configured to use the remote backend
- CSS and JS assets are properly configured for MIME types

## Deployment Trigger
This file ensures proper static site configuration for Render.com deployment.